Estava a ver os pássaros.

345
00:32:19,080 --> 00:32:22,550
Sim. Sim.

346
00:32:26,120 --> 00:32:27,951
Está a ver?

347
00:32:40,200 --> 00:32:42,634
Por que não falaste antes?

348
00:32:43,280 --> 00:32:44,474
Eu...

349
00:32:49,080 --> 00:32:50,718
Estava assustado.

350
00:32:54,320 --> 00:32:55,469
Tive medo.

351
00:32:57,640 --> 00:32:58,709
Cobarde.

352
00:33:37,520 --> 00:33:39,397
Vamos.

353
00:33:39,560 --> 00:33:43,269
